    "name": "Condenado: Sem Saída",
    "steam_appid": 3307350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/fb80ccc7461a87e21daf63e3d601bc4a.avif?t=1768418753\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Condemned: No Scape</strong> is a love letter to the golden age of the Game Boy, but with the brutal precision of modern platformers. You wake up in a forgotten prison, with no memories and only one goal: escape. But the exit isn't just a door… it's a choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/4f6eb1caea5015dcaf247a1a408e4619.poster.avif?t=1768418753\" width=400 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/4f6eb1caea5015dcaf247a1a408e4619.webm?t=1768418753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/4f6eb1caea5015dcaf247a1a408e4619.mp4?t=1768418753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/c9f8fbc2dc6f8dc982f4d6312d7475a4.avif?t=1768418753\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Forget luck. Here, every pixel counts.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight Controls:</strong> Physics designed to respond instantly to your reflexes. If you die, it's on you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Environment is Your Enemy:</strong> Crumbling platforms, invisible spikes, and traps that demand perfect timing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Instant Respawn:</strong> Died? Try again immediately. Frustration is part of the learning process.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/8cae33d463ee04ba6fbb2239b68c1716.poster.avif?t=1768418753\" width=400 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/8cae33d463ee04ba6fbb2239b68c1716.webm?t=1768418753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/8cae33d463ee04ba6fbb2239b68c1716.mp4?t=1768418753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/03a9988851067c02b5573ccd9a1dfc3b.avif?t=1768418753\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlike other games in the genre, your journey isn't empty.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> Your actions and discoveries define the protagonist's fate. Will you just run, or will you uncover the truth?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expanded Lore:</strong> Find documents and clues scattered across the map to understand who built this place and why you are here.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/98762914d357c25be45e591c73045a6b.avif?t=1768418753\" width=521 height=396 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/e99fa1eaad545c99e65c63d433d37116.avif?t=1768418753\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mastered the mechanics? Prove it.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Native Speedrun Mode:</strong> The game features a built-in timer and tools for those looking to break records.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fluid Level Design:</strong> Levels built with &quot;flow&quot; in mind. When you master the game, it becomes a dance of speed and precision.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/61ac39f052e7fe7080ff63d14c5d059c.avif?t=1768418753\" width=704 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307350/extras/9ddd6c507e08093be5fe4e701b77359b.avif?t=1768418753\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro-Modern Aesthetic:</strong> Authentic 8-bit pixel art enriched with volumetric lighting and HD post-processing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully Voiced Narrative:</strong> Original voice acting (PT-BR) brings life (and death) to the characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fluid &amp; Precise Gameplay:</strong> Every jump and movement must be calculated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Soundtrack:</strong> Chiptune mixed with darkwave synths to create constant tension.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mysterious Environments:</strong> Hidden secrets that encourage exploration and discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escalating Challenge:</strong> Making every new level more engaging and rewarding.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single Player experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75 Levels divided into 3 Acts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Game Modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret Areas to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HD Cutscenes &amp; Voice Acting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Native Speedrun Mode.</p></li></ul>",
